room_title: Escape room "Sweet Shoppe" by Challenge Escape Rooms in New York
room_description: You've been practicing in the kitchen like crazy, determined to win a TV baking competition that starts in an hour. All of your friends have already left for the show set, and as you get ready to go, you realize they've locked you inside the bakery! The extra key could be anywhere... Will you make it out in time for the competition?
